54.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Black-Keys-Gallagher@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Black-Keys-Gallagher@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Black-Keys-Gallagher@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Black-Keys-Gallagher@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">Noel Gallagher</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-black-keys">The Black Keys</a>一起在<em>Later…With Jools Holland</em>中表演了他们的歌曲“On The Game”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-32-noel-gallagher-beck-tour-tickets-indie-sleaze-strokes-glastonbury-3431217">黑键乐队谈论重返英国和他们的“史诗”新专辑</a></strong></li></ul><p>这场表演在周末的标志性音乐节目中进行，并于周六晚上（6 月 1 日）由 BBC 播出。在这一集中，黑键乐队以嘉宾身份加入了 Holland，并演唱了他们最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-black-keys-ohio-players-review-3612585">《Ohio Players》</a>中的几首歌曲。</p><p>首先，他们演奏了 LP 中的主打单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-new-single-beautiful-people-stay-high-and-announce-album-ohio-players-featuring-noel-gallagher-beck-3569722">《Beautiful People (Stay High)》</a> ，该单曲是他们在一月份发布专辑时发布的。接下来是“On The Game”的演绎，他们与英伦流行偶像、前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲</a>明星诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 一起表演。</p><p>当晚的合作是因为加拉格尔被认为是这首歌以及专辑中其他歌曲的共同创作者：《You&#39;ll Pay》和《Only Love Matters》。这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">High Flying Birds</a>主唱还为整张唱片的剪辑提供了和声和电吉他。</p><p>在此之际，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dan-auerbach">丹·奥尔巴赫</a>和帕特里克·卡尼组成的美国二人组最近结束了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-add-third-london-brixton-academy-show-to-spring-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-3609204">他们的“国际球员巡回赛”的英国和爱尔兰站</a>。 </p><p><iframe title="黑键壮举。 Noel Gallagher - On The Game（后来...与 Jools Holland）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/xDniqhrUxPM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe title="The Black Keys - Beautiful People (Stay High) (稍后...与 Jools Holland)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/min8cqEPy5g?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>加拉格尔与 The Black Keys 的表演是<em>Later…With Jools Holland 的</em>一部分，几周前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-noel-gallagher-join-the-black-keys-on-stage-at-london-brixton-academy-3754426">他与 The Black Keys 一起参加了他们在伦敦的一场演出</a>。 5 月 7 日，在两人在布里克斯顿 O2 Academy Brixton 举行的三场演出中的第一场演出中，乐队邀请了这位前 Oasis 音乐家与他们一起进行安可演出。</p><p>在此之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-32-noel-gallagher-beck-tour-tickets-indie-sleaze-strokes-glastonbury-3431217">The Black Keys 去年接受了<em>NME</em>采访</a>，回忆了他们在录音室与这位“不可思议”的词曲作者合作的时光。</p><p> “他很搞笑，而且非常有才华，”卡尼说。 “我们称他为‘和弦大师’，因为他是一位完美主义者。”</p><p>他继续说道：“丹和我都是他和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆</a>的忠实粉丝。事实上，Liam 的歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/liam-gallagher-dave-grohl-new-song-everythings-electric-3153212">《Everything&#39;s Electric》</a>正是我们决定与 [制作人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/greg-kurstin">Greg] Kurstin</a>合作的原因。”</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">High Flying Birds</a>主唱后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-says-songs-hes-co-written-with-the-black-keys-are-fucking-amazing-3455959">称他贡献的三首 Black Keys 歌曲“太棒了”</a> 。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-black-keys-ohio-players-review-3612585">《Ohio Players》的三星级评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>将加拉格尔主打的《On The Game》描述为“甜蜜的吉他即兴演奏”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Noel Gallagher 谈“议会天空”、人工智能绿洲、1975 年和英国脱欧" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qUl5BVqtNZU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>至于这张专辑的整体，它的结论是：“黑键乐队可能拥有杀手级的唱片收藏，但《俄亥俄玩家》是一支可能太擅长做自己的乐队的作品。”</p><p>在有消息称乐队将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-as-the-black-keys-cancel-entire-2024-north-america-arena-tour-3759504">取消整个北美巡演</a>之后，Jools Holland 也出现了。</p><p>最初<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-as-the-black-keys-cancel-entire-2024-north-america-arena-tour-3759504">这个消息让粉丝们感到沮丧</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-break-silence-explain-why-cancel-north-american-tour-3759601">成员们后来公开了取消的消息</a>，称该计划已被取消并重新规划，以支持<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-add-third-london-brixton-academy-show-to-spring-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-3609204">他们最近欧洲约会中较小的剧院场地</a>。</p><p> “乐队希望向所有人保证丹和帕特里克还活着并且安然无恙，”他们的声明开始了。</p><p> “继最近在英国和欧洲举行的一系列演出之后，包括在布里克斯顿学院和巴黎 Zenith 等标志性场馆停留之后，我们决定对‘国际球员’巡回赛的北美站进行一些改变，这将使我们能够为歌迷和乐队提供同样令人兴奋、亲密的体验，并将很快宣布修改后的日期。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-noel-gallagher-join-the-black-keys-to-perform-on-the-game-on-later-with-jools-holland-3761896">观看 Noel Gallagher 与 The Black Keys 一起在“Later…With Jools Holland”中表演“On The Game”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
布拉德·皮特和安吉丽娜·朱莉的女儿试图将皮特从名字中删除https://www.nme.com/news/film/brad-pitt-and-angelina-jolies-daughter-seeks-to-drop-pitt-from-name-3761864?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=brad-pitt-安吉丽娜·朱利斯的女儿寻求除掉皮特的名字Sam WarnerMon, 03 Jun 2024 09:49:50 +0000 Film NewsNews.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3761864 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希洛·朱莉-皮特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Shiloh 在年满 18 岁时提交了请愿书</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/brad-pitt-and-angelina-jolies-daughter-seeks-to-drop-pitt-from-name-3761864">布拉德·皮特和安吉丽娜·朱莉的女儿试图将皮特从名字中删除的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希洛·朱莉-皮特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brad-pitt">布拉德·皮特</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/angelina-jolie">安吉丽娜·朱莉</a>的女儿希洛·努维尔·朱莉·皮特已请求将皮特从她的姓氏中删除。</p><p>希洛是这对前好莱坞夫妇的第三个孩子，她于上周一（5 月 27 日）向洛杉矶县高等法院提交了请愿书，当时她已经年满 18 岁了。</p><p>根据请愿书（来自<a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/story/2024-05-31/angelina-jolie-brad-pitt-shiloh-petition-drop-father-last-name" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《洛杉矶时报</em></a>》），她希望被称为希洛·努维尔·朱莉（Shiloh Nouvel Jolie）。</p><p>此前，皮特和朱莉的另外两个孩子似乎与皮特的名字保持了距离，大女儿扎哈拉在一段 Alpha Kappa Alpha 联谊会视频（来自<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CzsJpzar3s1/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Essence</em></a> ）中介绍自己为“扎哈拉·马利·朱莉”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3761894" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3761894" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3761894" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Angelina-Jolie-and-Brad-Pitt.jpg" alt="安吉丽娜·朱莉和布拉德·皮特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Angelina-Jolie-and-Brad-Pitt.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Angelina-Jolie-and-Brad-Pitt-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Angelina-Jolie-and-Brad-Pitt-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Angelina-Jolie-and-Brad-Pitt-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Angelina-Jolie-and-Brad-Pitt-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Angelina-Jolie-and-Brad-Pitt-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3761894" class="wp-caption-text">安吉丽娜·朱莉和布拉德·皮特。图片来源：Getty/Jason LaVeris</figcaption></figure><p>据<a href="https://people.com/angelina-jolie-brad-pitt-daughter-vivienne-drops-pitt-from-name-playbill-8654120" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志</em></a>报道，女儿薇薇安最近也从百老汇戏剧<em>《局外人》</em>的剧单中删除了皮特这个名字。</p><p>皮特和朱莉的离婚诉讼正在进行中，朱莉于 2016 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/angelina-jolie-alleges-physical-abuse-by-brad-pitt-in-new-lawsuit-3322996">在一架私人飞机上发生肢体冲突</a>后提出离婚，据称他们的一个孩子马迪克斯也卷入了这一事件。</p><p>皮特因涉嫌事件而受到“虐待儿童调查”，洛杉矶儿童和家庭服务部<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/brad-pitt-cleared-child-abuse-claims-1841236">后来澄清了演员的不当行为</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/angelina-jolie-alleges-physical-abuse-by-brad-pitt-in-new-lawsuit-3322996">2022 年，在针对联邦调查局的匿名投诉中，朱莉被发现是原告，联邦调查局已经结束了对皮特涉嫌家庭暴力的调查，之后，涉嫌争吵的细节进一步曝光</a>。皮特否认了所有不当行为的指控。</p><p>这对前夫妇还卷入了法国米拉瓦尔酒庄的纠纷，皮特于 2022 年起诉朱莉，指控她未经朱莉事先同意就出售了自己在该酒庄的股份。 </p><figure id="attachment_3761895" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3761895" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3761895" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Angelina-Jolie-and-Brad-Pitt-1.jpg" alt="安吉丽娜·朱莉和布拉德·皮特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Angelina-Jolie-and-Brad-Pitt-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Angelina-Jolie-and-Brad-Pitt-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Angelina-Jolie-and-Brad-Pitt-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Angelina-Jolie-and-Brad-Pitt-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Angelina-Jolie-and-Brad-Pitt-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Angelina-Jolie-and-Brad-Pitt-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3761895" class="wp-caption-text">安吉丽娜·朱莉和布拉德·皮特。图片来源：盖蒂/巴里·金</figcaption></figure><p>朱莉声称皮特阻止了她出售该房产，并且只有在他同意“更繁重”和“更广泛”的保密协议的情况下才会同意。朱莉此前曾建议皮特希望她签署一份保密协议，以阻止她说出他涉嫌虐待她和她的孩子的行为。</p><p>今年早些时候，朱莉的律师<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/angelina-jolies-lawyers-call-brad-pitts-nda-request-abusive-3751481">将皮特试图与第三方获得她过去的保密协议的行为称为“滥用”</a> 。</p><p>今年四月，朱莉的律师<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/angelina-jolie-makes-fresh-abuse-claims-against-brad-pitt-3613761">声称皮特在飞机事件之前曾有身体虐待行为</a>，皮特的代表拒绝对新的虐待指控发表评论。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/brad-pitt-and-angelina-jolies-daughter-seeks-to-drop-pitt-from-name-3761864">布拉德·皮特和安吉丽娜·朱莉的女儿试图将皮特从名字中删除的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
