tty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_katyperry_harrisonbutker_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_katyperry_harrisonbutker_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_katyperry_harrisonbutker_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_katyperry_harrisonbutker_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/katy-perry">凯蒂·佩里</a>重新编辑了堪萨斯城酋长队踢球手哈里森·巴特克最近颇具争议的毕业典礼演讲。</p><p>本月早些时候，巴特克在本笃会学院的毕业典礼上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-kelces-teammate-quotes-taylor-swift-while-criticising-working-women-and-pride-3756998">发表了颇具争议的毕业典礼演讲</a>，批评职业女性和骄傲。巴特克在演讲中建议女性应该扮演家庭主妇和家庭主妇的角色，而不是追逐事业。</p><p>现在，佩里在她的 Instagram 上分享了一个经过编辑的版本，以纪念骄傲月，其中显示巴特克庆祝观众中即将大学毕业的“女士们”，并指出她们“应该为[她们]为此所取得的成就感到自豪指向[他们]年轻的生活”。</p><p> “为我的女儿们、我的毕业生和我的同性恋者解决了这个问题——你们可以做任何事情，恭喜你，并感到高兴，”她写道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C7sSJyovXU7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 